@startuml
[*] -> GreetUser : User arrives
GreetUser -> CheckPIN : Card inserted
CheckPIN -> CorrectPIN : PIN correct
CorrectPIN -> DisplayOptions : Display options (withdraw, check info, transfer)
DisplayOptions -> ProcessRequest : User selects request
ProcessRequest -> EndSession : Request processed

CheckPIN -> IncorrectPIN : PIN incorrect
IncorrectPIN -> TryAgain : Try again
TryAgain -> CheckPIN : Card still inserted
CheckPIN -> InvalidCard : Card invalid or too many incorrect PINs
InvalidCard -> KeepCard : Keep card for security
KeepCard -> ReturnCard : User cancels
ReturnCard -> EndSession : End session

@enduml
